The package boost-type-erasure is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS type_erasure)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::type_erasure)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_type_erasure REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::type_erasure)
